---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Moritz Bierling and Statecraft Systems.">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <section class="section">
    <p>
      Statecraft Systems was founded by Moritz Bierling, a systems architect and strategist focused on the design of institutions, brands, and operational frameworks for communities committed to sovereignty and responsible cooperation.
    </p>

    <p>
      Bierling brings experience across distributed systems, organizational design, strategic communication, and formation practices. His work has included advising civic resilience initiatives, designing governance structures for decentralized organizations, and building institutional infrastructure for communities aligned on principles of reciprocal obligation and local responsibility.
    </p>

    <p>
      In addition to Statecraft Systems, Bierling contributes to the wider ecosystem through:
    </p>

    <ul style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md); margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); color: var(--text-primary);">
      <li style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);"><strong>Modern Minuteman:</strong> Co-founder and lead architect of training and formation programs for distributed civic resilience.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);"><strong>The Field Company:</strong> Advisor and consultant on systems design and organizational operations.</li>
      <li><strong>Personal work:</strong> Writing, research, and consulting on systems architecture, institutions, and the conditions for human flourishing.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      More information about Moritz Bierling's work, writing, and consulting practice can be found at:
    </p>

    <div class="contact-block" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);">
      <a href="https://moritzbierling.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">moritzbierling.com</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
